            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>most</strong> of the <strong>diced red onion</strong> (save some for garnish!) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5 min or until softened</p>",
