      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the<strong> tomato paste</strong>,<strong> chipotle paste</strong>,<strong> soy sauce </strong>and 150ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until thickened</p><p>Once thickened, stir through the <strong>sour cream </strong>and cook for 1-2 min further – this is your <strong>creamy chipotle salsa</strong></p>",
